IMPORTANT DATA DISCLAIMER:

This software uses completely synthetic, randomly-generated data for
demonstration and research purposes only. It does NOT contain real Swiss
parliamentary data, government information, or factual political relationships.

Do NOT use this application for:
- Actual political analysis
- Real transparency reporting
- Publishing as official data
- Any purpose assuming data authenticity

For real Swiss political information, consult official sources:
- https://www.parlament.ch (Swiss Parliament)
- https://www.bfs.admin.ch (Federal Statistics Office)
- https://www.shab.ch (Swiss Business Registry)
